    "AlexNet was introduced by Alex Krizhevsky.",
    "In 2012, AlexNet competed in ImageNet Large Scale Visual Recognition Challenge.",
    "AlexNet won the competition and was at par then the opponent.",
    "AlexNet was able to get 15.3% top-5 error which was 10.8% lower then the opponent.",
    "AlexNet requires more depth in its architecture as compare to LeNet."
  ]
